writer.name: 古德蒙达尔·阿诺尔·古德蒙松 Guðmundur Arnar Guðmundsson

director.name: 古德蒙达尔·阿诺尔·古德蒙松 Guðmundur Arnar Guðmundsson

introduction: Jeffrey, a young African American in Iceland participates in a self-help group with the hope of winning back his girlfriend. The self-help group is managed by Beth, a self-educated new age therapist that uses strange methods to reach her goals. As the program progresses, Jeffrey has difficulties figuring out if Beth is really trying to help him get back his girlfriend or not.
